const UserItem *  user,
const ClientSetting *  clientSetting
)  [virtual]
 

Checks if positions should be pushed and does that and also might say that positions doesn't have to be stored in db as they already has been pushed.

Parameters:
p The positions.
user The user that the positions are from.
clientSetting The client the user is using, may be NULL.
Returns:
0 if ok, 1 if positions mustn't be stored in db -1 if error and -2 if timeout.
